      <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-pencil-square me-2 text-accent"></i> Updated profile email ‚Äî 2025-09-20</li>
      <li><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right me-2 text-accent"></i> Logged in ‚Äî 2025-09-18</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

